OL,3,CMan, 45, jailed for choking woman
OL,4,Cuntil she nearly passed out
OL,6,FA 45-year-old man has been sentenced
OL,7,Fto more than four and a half years in
OL,8,Fprison after throwing a woman to the
OL,9,Fground before choking and hitting her,
OL,10,Fand separately stealing from a
OL,11,Fjewellery shop.
OL,13,FAndrew Page was found guilty of grave
OL,14,Fand criminal assault and theft at
OL,15,FJersey's Royal Court, he also received
OL,16,Fa seven-year Domestic Abuse Protection
OL,17,FOrder which can ban him from
OL,18,Fcontacting the woman or being within a
OL,19,Fcertain distance of her.
