OL,3,CMan, 45, jailed for choking woman
OL,4,Cuntil she nearly passed out
OL,6,FIn December 2022 at a residential
OL,7,Faddress on island, Page threw the
OL,8,Fwoman to the ground before placing his
OL,9,Fhands around her neck several times
OL,10,Fand choking her until she nearly lost
OL,11,Fconsciousness.
OL,13,FPage also hit the woman's head against
OL,14,Fa skirting board and wall before
OL,15,Fleaving the property.
OL,17,FHe initially accused the woman of
OL,18,Fassaulting him but Page was proved to
OL,19,Fbe the attacker.
