OL,3,CMan, 45, jailed for choking woman
OL,4,Cuntil she nearly passed out
OL,6,FDetective Constable Verity Thomas from
OL,7,FJersey Police's Public Protection Unit
OL,8,Fsays: "This was a deliberate and nasty
OL,9,Fassault carried out by Page. Behaviour
OL,10,Flike this should never be tolerated.
OL,12,F"We will do everything in our power to
OL,13,Fsee offenders such as this face
OL,14,Fjustice. Anyone else who has
OL,15,Fexperienced similar abuse can come
OL,16,Fforward and speak to officers at any
OL,17,Ftime."
